OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew school attendance hubs 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flaunched                   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New "attendance hubs" are being        
OL,6, launched in London to help reduce      
OL,7, persistent school absences, the        
OL,8, Department for Education (DfE) says.   
OL,10,FThe DfE has chosen nine London schools 
OL,11,Fwith "excellent attendance" rates to   
OL,12,Fshare ideas with others across England.
OL,14,FIt is also establishing a #15m scheme  
OL,15,Foffering "direct support" to           
OL,16,Fpersistently absent pupils and their   
OL,17,Ffamilies across England.               
OL,19,FAn advertising campaign has been set up
OL,20,Fto coincide with the scheme.           
